{"tid":1656044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌晒你地老母廢閪香港人","createTime":"2019-10-15T11:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T11:30:00.000Z","uid":61122,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d50bcd9aa56bd6c249589d36256ffc3c890dba18","tid":1656044,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"口講點嬲點嬲，返現實世界就做順民，屌你地老母出街個罩都係唔敢，怕咩俾人拉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊撚柒個唔怕俾人拉呀</span></span>人地一埋毛都未出齊既𡃁仔都戴罩返學，反觀大人，一個都唔見<br />\n屌你地老母淨係識助養，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">課幾多都冇撚用啦，淨係俾錢，而唔將抗爭帶入生活，你地同推班𡃁仔去送新屋嶺冇撚分別，係你地送班𡃁仔俾狗屌</span></span><br />\n蒙面法係唔俾我地遊行集會戴嘢，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日常生活狗只係有權叫你除罩望下你，冇權拉你，你唔舒服係有權戴罩</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">清楚未呀豬閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"95cfbd46b7e8a7baddcde9224461c8eee35b7d56","tid":1656044,"uid":61122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"推埋十月二十要出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fT71hCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfT71hCv.jpg&h=2ed785a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aHsXCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aHsXCw.jpg&h=a4b2798a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzOLKhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzOLKhw.jpg&h=624586ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmBaaXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmBaaXx.jpg&h=9bbf0937&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dSdcphy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdSdcphy.jpg&h=34006484&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmG114e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmG114e.jpg&h=012f04db&s={SIZE}\"